The paper discusses the intelligence measure of cognitive radios, which involves the use of machine learning and signal processing techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
